00:03:56.400 --> 00:03:59.850
but only Kunugigaoka has students who'd be fun to take on

00:03:59.850 --> 00:04:01.930
in one-on-one academic showdowns.

00:04:03.130 --> 00:04:06.600
I'll have no problem getting the job I'm after,

00:04:07.350 --> 00:04:10.810
