00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:29.830
We're each going our own way.

00:04:30.440 --> 00:04:34.230
My top pick is Keisetsu University's prep school.

00:04:34.620 --> 00:04:40.500
It's crazy tough, but it's the best shortcut for getting into the college Mom wanted to send me to.

00:04:41.090 --> 00:04:43.700
After college, though...

00:04:44.840 --> 00:04:48.280
With these odd, anachronistic talents of mine,

00:04:48.760 --> 00:04:52.100
I'm not sure what I can be, or even what I want to be.

00:04:53.010 --> 00:04:56.340
